Decided to dress up like a cocaine dealer today...

Jk i don't trade cocaine for money.

I only trade poems for money.

-----
Babe do you really think I could trade cocaine?

In a world full of people that only try to sell?

On social media that feels icy cold,

It's your boo BeerBiceps that knows your heart too well...

----

You've fought and worked and cried and toiled,

Only to view mostly mediocrity on your phone.

At the end of a hard day's work, my love...

I will ensure my reels will make you say - "I've grown!"

----
And when you try to sleep at night,

Fashion Bhaiyya's alter ego starts to shine so bright!

Of death and ghosts and aliens aplenty,

He'll serve you darkness same as he serves you light.

----

Is he a self obsessed d*ckhead capitalist?

No, he's just a boy with rampant ADHD.

Who enjoys the money as much as he enjoys the attention,

But his true nature - only do long time followers see. 🏝

----

~ Randu signing off.

You read that right, my stage name is the same as my childhood nickname.

Speaking to the Indian Marine Commando Legend, @vijaypalsingh9173 was one of the most exhilarating experiences of my life.

Lots of us know about the Army's Special Forces - The Para SF.

But very few know details about the Indian Navy's Special Forces - The Marcos or Marine Commandos.

This is a tiny snippet from the 2 podcasts (1 Hindi, 1 English) that we recorded with Vijay sir.

Underwater combat, night diving, taking on sea snakes, swimming with sharks, getting stung by jelly fish, neutralising a ship full of terrorists, AND A LOT MORE.

What an insane life this Navy veteran has lived!!! 

One of my favourite guests. Humble and calm on the outside. Sharp, observant and deadly on the inside.

Thank you for the podcasts and thank you for your service, Vijay Sir! Jai Hind! 🇮🇳🇮🇳🇮🇳

#IndianNavy #marinecommandos #commando #specialforces #TheRanveerShow
